[SHORT DESC]
Prevents the enemy from lowering this Pokémon's Attack. Increases Cut's area of effect.
[LONG DESC]
<p>This Pokémon is immune to the enemy lowering its Attack stat. Does not block self-inflicted Attack drops, such as the Attack drop from Superpower.</p>

<p>If a Pokémon with this ability is in your party and the move Cut is used while in a grassy area, more grass will be removed than usual.</p>